    "Id": "chassisdef_quark_QRK-D",
    "Name": "Quark",
    "Details": "The D configuration is built around battlefield support and electronic warfare rather than direct firepower. A Narc Missile Beacon in the right torso tags enemy units for allied missile fire, while an ECM Suite in the left torso denies targeting data to opponents. An LRM 5 in the right arm and twin ER Small Lasers in the left arm provide minimal self-defense. Speed is the primary defensive tool.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Communications</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.98</color></b>",
