  "StockRole": "Scout",
  "YangsThoughts": "Twenty tons, Clan Omni, running at over 120 kph. Speed like that on a frame this light — it is impressive engineering, I will give Clan Burrock that. Shame about the Dark Caste connection. The pod space is tight at seven tons, so every config is making hard choices. Some do it well. Some less so. Whoever pilots one needs to keep moving and stay smart about range.",
